entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: Vayde's jobs have been completed and enough information has been gathered for Dathnaeya to make a well informed decision regarding the Rebel Alliance.
entries.journal_entry_description: All missions at the N.S.H. base have been completed.  All that is left is to report back to Trezya followed by Cpt. Quellium.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Are the requests made by Vayde and Trezya fulfilled?
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Speak with Captain Quellium at the hidden Rebel office in Dearic.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Return to Trezya Nenei at the hidden Rebel office and report that her friend has been rescued.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Secured, the supplies now need to be returned to Captain Quellium.
